        <p>You can set the default behavior for a  wired source connected to the HDMI-in port of a Solstice Gen3 Pod. This is useful if you wish to utilize a persistent wired input source such as a dedicated in-room computer, an integrated video room system device, or a digital signage media player between collaboration sessions.</p>
